<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP Verification - MediWay</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            table-layout: fixed;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .main-card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #eeeeee;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #007bff; /* MediWay Blue */
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #444444;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .otp-container {
            background-color: #f0f7ff;
            border: 2px dashed #007bff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 25px 0;
            padding: 15px 40px;
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .expiry-text {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999999;
        }
        .brand {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <center>
            <div style="height: 40px;"></div>
            <div class="main-card">
                <div class="header">
                    <h1>MediWay <span style="color: #28a745;">Health Care</span></h1>
                </div>

                <div class="content">
                    <div class="greeting">Hello, <strong><%= name %></strong>!</div>
                    <p>Use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to complete your verification process.</p>
                    
                    <div class="otp-container">
                        <h2 class="otp-code"><%= otp %></h2>
                    </div>

                    <p class="expiry-text">This code is valid for 2 minutes only.</p>
                    
                    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #777; margin-top: 30px;">
                        If you did not request this code, please ignore this email or contact our support.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer">
                <p>&copy; 2026 <span class="brand">MediWay Health Care</span>. All Rights Reserved.</p>
                <p>Providing Quality Health Services</p>
            </div>
        </center>
    </div>
</body>
</html>